1 for Higher Education or the Liaison Council on Medical Education.
2 The physician members shall have actively practiced as licensed
3 physicians continuously in this state for the three (3) years
4 immediately preceding their appointment to the Board. All members
5 of the Board shall be residents of this state and shall be appointed
6 by the Governor as provided for in Section 482 of this title. All
7 present members of the Board shall continue to serve for the
8 remainder of their current terms.
